text: KBZI (106.1 FM) is a radio station licensed to Mooreland, Oklahoma, United States. The station is currently owned by Robert Young. KBZI broadcasts an 80's Rock format to the Woodward, Oklahoma, area. ==History== This station was assigned call sign KBZI on January 24, 2017. ==References== ==External links== BZI Category:Radio stations established in 2017 Category:2017 establishments in Oklahoma
